songs.title: Faribolana
songs.content:
{start_of_verse}
[C]Olona samihafa l[F]oko
samih[G]afa firaz[F]ànan[C]a
Tsy t[C]ia mitsitokot[F]oko
fa m[G]ifandray t[F]ànan[C]a
[Dm]Samy leo sy m[G]ahatsapa
fa r[G]atsy ny miz[F]araz[C]ara
[Dm]Ka aleo ir[G]ay lapa
mit[G]ovy zo mit[F]ovy anj[C]ara
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_verse}
Ireo tanana izay mifandray
toa sarotra sarahana
Toa miloko rano iray
tsy hita ho havahana
Toy ny ankizy miara milalao 
toa lavitry ny olana
Jereo ireto izy malaina hifandao
manao faribolana
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_verse}
Dia mihodina tsy misy fiafarany
miodidina fitiavana
Fa tsara sy mamy aok’izany
izany hoe mifampihavana
Hadino hoe Rakoto ilay mavomavo 
Rabe ilay manana
Fa samy hazoto hanandratra
izany fihavanana
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_verse}
Jereko ny manodidina ahy
toa mianjona mangarika
Antsoiko hoe ndao isika hiray
tsy misy voasarika
Fa misy ny loko tsy mety hifangaro,
misy harena tsy hihavanana
Dia mitsitokotoko miala amin’ny maro
ny fotsy sy ireo manana
{end_of_verse}

songs.title: Ry Tompo
songs.content:
{start_of_verse}
Ry T[D]ompo 
Ry T[G]ompo 
[A]--Omeo hery [D]aho
Ho entiko han[D]ompo, han[G]ompo
[A]--Ny anaran[D]ao
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_verse}
Fa n[Gm7]y fakam-pan[D/F#]ahy
Mbol[Gm7]a mananontanona [D/F#]ahy
Ny f[Bm7]itiava-t[F#m7]ena
Maham[Am]enatra jer[G]ena
Vonjeo aho ry t[A]ompo
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_verse}
Ry raiko (x2)
Omeo toromarika

{end_of_verse}

Fa hanao ny tsara
Mba tsy ho ratsy fiafara
Matoky anao ry Tompo. 
{end_of_verse}

songs.title: Farakely
songs.content:
{start_of_verse}
[G]--Tonga [Am7]aho dia nan[Bm7]orok[G]a 
[C]--Ny t[D]akolak[G]ao 
[C]--Nefa ian[Bm7]ao toa ts[Am7]y mba nangoraka [C]ahy 
[Em7]--Angamba k[D]osa efa l[G]ao 
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_verse}
Mba hitanao tokoa va re 
Ireto masoko mitoloko 
o ! o ! o ! 
Mitady fitiavana be dia be 
Mba hampitony ny foko
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_chorus}
[Am7]--Nangarika f[Bm7]otsiny [C]--ian[G]ao 
[Am7]--Ka nan[Bm7]ao jado-t[D]ongotra 
[Am7]--Malama an[C]ie ny lalana [G]--ho diavin[Em7]ao
[C]--Ka sao ian[D]ao ho potrak[G]a
[G]o ! [Am7]o ! [G/B]o ! 
[Am7]--Malama an[C]ie ny lalana [G]--ho diavin[Em7]ao
[C]--Ka sao ian[D]ao ho potrak[G]a
{end_of_chorus}
{start_of_verse}
Dia handao ahy tokoa ve ianao 
Ry Farakely
o ! o ! ! 
Fo maratra anie no sisa navelanao 
o ! o ! o ! 
{end_of_verse}
{start_of_chorus}
Nefa ianao sao mihevitra 
Fa izaho hanaraka anao 
Ry Farakely mahalasa eritreritra 
Zory ny lalanao o ! o! o! 
Ry Farakely mahalasa eritreritra 
Zory ny lalanao
[]{end_of_chorus}

songs.title: Ny lasantsika
songs.content:
[D]–Ny l[C6]asants[G/B]ika–[Bb6]
[D]–Tsy hay h[G]ofaf[A]ana
[D]–Tsy mety m[C6]angats[G/B]iaka–[Bb6]
Fa tad[D]idik[G]o maz[A]an[D]a
[Gm]–Ireo safos[D/F#]afo
[Em]–Sy angolang[Bm]ola
[F/G#]–Namela [A]afo
[A#7]–Tsy mety t[A]ola


Toa tsy tantin’ny saina ny mieritreritra fa
Ianao ilay nolalaina mitampify an-tratran’olon-kafa
Ireo teny mamiko naverinao ho azy
Hay izy ireny tamiko mbola vazivazy


Izaho no namafy, ny hafa no nijinja
Izao indray no niafy fa nilaozanao nifindra
Natao lamba tonta aho, natsipy toa rovi-damba
Zary natontatonta,lany tsirony angamba


Ilay vatanao mangovitra raha tojo hafaliana
Ny ambany miovitrovitra, tsara karakaran’olon-tiana
Ny rangotrangotrao tratra hafa no ratrainy
Reo antsoantsonao, ny molotrao notsenainy


Tsy ilay nisolo toerana no ankahalaiko
Fitia tsy azo ferana, ny fahavaloko hajaiko
Fa ianao kosa mbola antenaiko
Mbola tsy afa-trosa, izaho ve dia hiala maina

songs.title: Hanaraka anao
songs.content:
Han[C]araka an[Am]ao,toy ny [E7]alok[Am]a
Ka ts[Dm7]y hifand[F/C]ao
Raha tsy andro tena m[G7/B]alok [G]a
Fa raha mb[C]ola m[Am]isy,tarap[E7]a-hazav[Dm]ana
Tsy hi[F]ala teo mih[Dm]itsy aho
Raha t[G]oa mbol[E7/Ab]a tam [Am]ana
[Am]Eny l[G]etsy [F]a!


Tsy andriko intsony,ny andro maraina
Azahoako hifoha,hamonjy anao ry aina
Ka tsy hiala teo indray,raha tsy ny andro no hariva
Nefa injay ny masoandro iva d iva


Izaho anie ka zaza,tsy mahasara-dreny
Hanaraka anao,eny rehetra eny
Ianao irery no afaka,ampitony ny tomany
Raha toa ho solafaka,ianao no hanarina ahy hatrany


Ny vavan'ny sasany,tsy ahoako intsony
Fa ny fitiavantsika no asandratro ambony
Ka ny vavaka atao,dia ny mba aharitra hatrany
Aharitra tokoa anie,zany fiarahtsika izany
